* factor out Source from Node
  make it use a FileIO
  move Text, Position etc. to a new module Source

* refactor separators: let nodes eat separators when they are pushed to the stack (like whitespace and comments).
  change to_ruby(whitespace = false) to to_ruby(context = false)
	remove separators from lists, calls etc. and namespaces from constants
	
* refactor RubyBuilder events to class methods on Ruby::Node classes
	e.g. Hash.on_paren would wrap into a Statement while ArgList.on_paren would set the delims

sexp("I18n::t()") # =>
[:program,
 [:stmts_add,
  [:stmts_new],
  [:method_add_arg,
   [:call,
    [:var_ref, [:@const, "I18n", [1, 0]]],
    :".",
    [:@ident, "t", [1, 6]]],
   [:arg_paren, nil]]]]

watch the separator!



